          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>No Tax Write-offs for Corporate Wrongdoers Act</strong></p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) deny a tax deduction for any amount paid or incurred for punitive damages in connection with any judgment in, or settlement of, any legal action; and (2) include any amount paid as punitive damages in gross income for income tax purposes. </p>]]></text>
